&lt;p&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;none&quot;&gt;Engineers Gate runs a global, follow-the-sun systematic trading operation across equities, futures, FX, fixed income, and credit. We are hiring a Trading Operations Associate to join our global team to sit at the intersection of the trading desk, operations, and engineering to own real-time monitoring of systematic trade flow, execution alerts, automated jobs, and data pipelines; to handle core trade lifecycle workflows including locates, trade capture, trade booking, stock loan recalls,&amp;nbsp;trade files and trade allocations;&amp;nbsp;and&amp;nbsp;to drive resolution of trade blotter breaks and executing-broker discrepancies.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-props=&quot;{&amp;quot;335559739&amp;quot;:280}&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
